request.description:
**Auth**: Patient (own released) OR Health Officer (all)
**Middleware**: authenticate
**Validation**: idParamValidation

Get the complete status change history for a specific test result.

**Patient Access**:
- Can only view if `result.patientProfileId === req.user.id`
- Can only view if `result.currentStatus === 'released'`

**Health Officer Access**:
- Can view status history for any result regardless of status

**Response** (200 OK):
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "resultId": "65f1234567890abcdef99999",
    "bookingId": "65f1234567890abcdef22222",
    "currentStatus": "released",
    "statusHistory": [
      {
        "status": "pending",
        "changedAt": "2026-02-27T08:30:00.000Z",
        "changedBy": {
          "_id": "...",
          "fullName": "Dr. Jane Smith"
        }
      },
      {
        "status": "released",
        "changedAt": "2026-02-27T14:30:00.000Z",
        "changedBy": {
          "_id": "...",
          "fullName": "Dr. John Doe"
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

**Use Case**: Track test result lifecycle, audit trail, patient transparency

